%N A017524 a(n) = (12*n)^4.
%H A017524 Paolo Xausa, <a href="/A017524/b017524.txt">Table of n, a(n) for n = 0..10000</a>
%H A017524 <a href="/index/Rec#order_05">Index entries for linear recurrences with constant coefficients</a>, signature (5,-10,10,-5,1).
%F A017524 From _Elmo R. Oliveira_, Jun 02 2026: (Start)
%F A017524 a(n) = 5*a(n-1) - 10*a(n-2) + 10*a(n-3) - 5*a(n-4) + a(n-5).
%F A017524 G.f.: 20736*x*(1 + x)*(1 + 10*x + x^2)/(1 - x)^5.
%F A017524 E.g.f.: 20736*x*(1 + 7*x + 6*x^2 + x^3)*exp(x).
%F A017524 a(n) = 20736*A000583(n) = 16*A016912(n) = A008594(n)^4 = A000583(A008594(n)). (End)
%t A017524 (12*Range[0,20])^4 (* _Harvey P. Dale_, Mar 30 2016 *)
